data.description: Beautiful custom built all brick home in well established neighborhood! Relax and enjoy front porch sitting on nice covered porch. Home offers a open concept floorplan, family room has fireplace surrounded by shiplap, wood mantel and gas logs. Spacious kitchen with quartz countertops, stainless appliances, soft close cabinets, island and dining area. Large primary bedroom with ensuite bathroom that has quartz countertops and dual sinks, soaking tub and separate shower. 2nd and 3rd bedroom share a hall bathroom. There is a office and another room that is currently being used as den/flex room. Two car garage and deck. Nice neighborhood and convenient to schools.$450,000
